BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Jubilee
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270605T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270605T215500
DTSTAMP:20260724T154921Z
UID:occ-405@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Opera
DESCRIPTION:An opera written and directed by Tazewell Thompson\, librettis
 t of Blue\, with a score by Dianne Adams McDowell.\n\nTazewell Thompson wr
 ote the libretto and directs\; his previous opera\, Blue\, written with co
 mposer Jeanine Tesori\, was named a New York Times Best in Classical Music
  pick for 2019. The score is by Dianne Adams McDowell\, the Broadway vocal
  arranger behind A Gentleman's Guide to Love & Murder. The piece has alrea
 dy been staged at Arena Stage and Seattle Opera\; this production comes fr
 om The Atlanta Opera.
GEO:33.7439061;-84.4168227
LAST-MODIFIED:20260724T154831Z
LOCATION:Ray Charles Performing Arts Center\, 900 West End Avenue Southwes
 t
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://tickets.atlantaopera.org/147042/147043
END:VEVENT
